{"tid":1297802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察員佐級協會去信梁君彥   嚴厲譴責譚文豪、 區諾軒","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:32:37.000Z","uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49ec5cb021c8680f64e4db769e797188a0e0b65b","tid":1297802,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467306-20190708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467306-20190708.htm&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=77aebfc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467306-20190708.htm&h=09a40616\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467306-20190708.htm</a><br />\n警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉去信立法會主席梁君彥，表示警方凌晨在旺角清場時，議員譚文豪及區諾軒刻意在警方防線前挑釁警方，以吸引記者聚集採訪，使場面更加混亂。協會認為兩人妨礙警察工作，不顧記者及其他行人安全，極度不負責任，對兩人非常失望及憤慨，並予以嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉形容，譚文豪以驕橫跋扈、野蠻無理的態度，以及粗鄙的動作言辭回應警方呼籲，令人髮指。又說有議員為個人立場和政治利益，刻意刁難前線警務人員，挑撥其他人的仇警情緒，帶頭製造矛盾及衝突 ，行徑及意圖令人切齒 。<br />\n<br />\n信件又提到，香港法例並沒有賦權立法會議員阻礙警務人員執法，表示有恃無恐的個別議員應立即停止阻礙或干預警方執行職務，請立法會主席正視個別議員操守問題。"},{"pid":"2a5ad84bb3b75adf6cb9ad7550c34565f9cd3c44","tid":1297802,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b246a9be7b4e590887dd3f4463faa6869cb6ec9","tid":1297802,"uid":267909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"唔知依家係邊個問題？<br />\n<br />\n明明係班狗自己有問題<br />\n兩個議員一句粗口都無，又無推無撞<br />\n<br />\n你可以唔理佢，係佢隔離過<br />\n但後面成班記者，唔通打記者？<br />\n<br />\n個警察公共關係出嚟講野時都玩野啦<br />\n口口講講唔係同議員講，係同傳媒講，但講完唔做野，扮晒咁<br />\n<br />\n比人捉晒衰左咩就到處寫信<br />\n<br />\n你老幾呀？一哥呀？定二哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7a67ff9c4a27c67316448671f35d77ac3fd514","tid":1297802,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:17:15.000Z","msg":"呢幾個會係員工福利會<br />\n唔係工會<br />\n淨係for警隊人員內部聯誼同員工福利，係冇資格對其他既議題指手劃腳，如果有，說明佢地已經超出左原本賦與佢地既權利，應予以解散及重組<br />\n同時立法會應盡快審視警隊，確保警隊的政治中立免受破壞，否則警隊是不應該再享有獨立於其他公務員的薪級表"},{"pid":"54a5958499a1b47be03d29fc096b467ae12d4f55","tid":1297802,"uid":199787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"最重要係立法會議員係高級過個爛9工會既所有會員，佢地憑乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760e538758c5535f2009bf4a4c44fc8b9357c81a","tid":1297802,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:23:13.000Z","msg":"俾記者錄低哂啦 兩位議員都冇做過咩 剩係問下有冇示威者係防暴後面 班狗係咁叫佢收皮 阻住佢地做野 跟住係咁推進 推9佢地同班記者"},{"pid":"5fcc22e119cc999b47d152ad9b024810797f652d","tid":1297802,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/2472874086133874?sfns=cl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F960526577368640%2Fposts%2F2472874086133874%3Fsfns%3Dcl&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c6c8b808\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/2472874086133874?sfns=cl</a><br />\n<br />\n警方新聞稿已出 歡迎留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好被件事咁快消化"},{"pid":"4e38b92d2a02abe92bdc1a75c9fd630c61d2244c","tid":1297802,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcc22e119cc999b47d152ad9b024810797f652d","tid":1297802,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/2472874086133874?sfns=cl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F960526577368640%2Fposts%2F2472874086133874%3Fsfns%3Dcl&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c6c8b808\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/2472874086133874?sfns=cl</a><br />\n<br />\n警方新聞稿已出 歡迎留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好被件事咁快消化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:32:37.000Z","msg":"佢大把野唔比人消化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}